Excellent course to reflect on the questions. The Mendoza school's ideologies do come through loud and clear, but we are given plenty of room to reflect and place our own thoughts into strong arguments. Not quite enough students participating in the active grading to make it quick enough, but overall good.
Wonderfully designed course! Can't recommend this course enough to anyone interetsed in going into business.
